{"tid":2253365,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"荷李活男星 Joseph Gordon-Levitt 貼抗爭詩邀港人錄音","createTime":"2020-10-22T06:03:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-22T06:03:51.000Z","uid":70629,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3326201f57da76bfac38ca3a9eb5ec120df269f5","tid":2253365,"uid":70629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T06:03:13.000Z","msg":"過去一年，香港經歷了抗暴之戰，引起國際關注，荷李活男星祖瑟夫哥頓利域（Joseph Gordon-Levitt）今年8月在fb向網民徵求香港靚相，計劃在網上平台hitRECord炮製一個關於香港的作品，他上個月再度在fb上載一張香港夜景照片，並再呼籲網民盡快提供照片。兩次均有不少網民在hitRECord瘋狂貼上反送中遊行和示威的照片，令網站變成一個國際文宣平台。剛剛祖瑟夫又再於fb呼籲香港人為一首詩錄音，詩中更擺明撐港人。<br />\n他於fb表示：「有香港人有興趣錄音嗎？我在找幾個人讀出以下幾句，你只需要一個電話！」該篇詩名為《香港永不眠》，翻譯如下：<br />\n<br />\n《香港永不眠》<br />\n香港，她永遠不眠<br />\n東方的美人<br />\n微笑的龍在呼吸<br />\n她是水中的火<br />\n載着靈魂與船隻的城市<br />\n香港，有自己的世界<br />\n當我們寫上自己的歷史<br />\n朝未知之路<br />\n但我們永不孤單<br />\n我們永遠都一條心<br />\n香港，雨中哭泣<br />\n人們因上街而在一起<br />\n自由的戰士<br />\n因痛楚的臉<br />\n聲音都會被聽見<br />\n香港，我們所有人的家<br />\n有景觀、海港與山嶺<br />\n在藍色的天與海之間<br />\n在清晰的日子<br />\n我們永遠都能看清楚<br />\n香港，我們的聖城<br />\n在大街小巷中走過談過<br />\n如此充滿生命力<br />\n這個我們安頓的地方<br />\n晚上都在發夢<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/SXTy1NSwGIsCbOc3VQK6cSnByiE=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TKEJYTXSNRBHLI4YBDWEKGY7VI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FSXTy1NSwGIsCbOc3VQK6cSnByiE%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTKEJYTXSNRBHLI4YBDWEKGY7VI.jpg&h=6a21e7ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/122455750_2739108696337202_8062959386441305774_o.jpg?_nc_cat=107&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=8bfeb9&amp;_nc_ohc=Xyn859OJzuwAX-wVKDS&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-1.fna&amp;oh=69dd555a66d12125a84cb4abfc6e8f5a&amp;oe=5FB4E3E9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F122455750_2739108696337202_8062959386441305774_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D107%26ccb%3D2%26_nc_sid%3D8bfeb9%26_nc_ohc%3DXyn859OJzuwAX-wVKDS%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-1.fna%26oh%3D69dd555a66d12125a84cb4abfc6e8f5a%26oe%3D5FB4E3E9&h=df35990e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/JoeGordonLevitt/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FJoeGordonLevitt%2F&d=mhl3ai6H9Odyk596tiaOPf2u4%2BaHFFj7NdFJeB1nj9U%3D&h=8df91abf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/JoeGordonLevitt/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9766a53b4f8467005613578de914bf92d1cc776c","tid":2253365,"uid":39710,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T06:03:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢都幾鐘意香港"}]}